00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:54,700
That man who used to pick up girls off
 the street? He doesn't exist anymore.

532
00:32:56,300 --> 00:32:58,200
And that girl that, uh, you're looking for?

533
00:32:59,800 --> 00:33:00,800
