00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:14,400
Particularly when there is
 so much future to look forward to?

537
00:33:18,100 --> 00:33:18,500
Wow...

538
00:33:21,100 --> 00:33:22,200
Let me see what I can do.

539
00:33:26,900 --> 00:33:28,100
