that machine was some sort of dark fantasy.

546
00:33:55,100 --> 00:33:57,500
I can feel the heat coming 
off your brain from here.

547
00:33:58,800 --> 00:33:59,800
What are you chewing on?

548
00:34:01,500 --> 00:34:04,300
Mm, nothing much. Just the mystery of life.

549
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:05,800
That again.

550
00:34:07,100 --> 00:34:11,200
You need to get your head out of the clouds
