551
00:34:11,600 --> 00:34:15,000
Mm...Are we really just the sum of our memories?

552
00:34:16,600 --> 00:34:19,900
Wait a second. I know the answer to that.
 I read it in a magazine.

553
00:34:23,100 --> 00:34:26,300
I mean, David Saunders,
he looks at his wife and he sees...

554
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:31,400
this wonderful woman that he met in the hospital
 while he was recovering from a horrible accident.

555
00:34:34,500 --> 00:34:36,500
