00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:41,200
No, this is nothing.

627
00:38:41,800 --> 00:38:43,000
This has nothing to do with us.

628
00:38:43,700 --> 00:38:46,500
They're just trying to find some missing people. Sh...

629
00:38:54,200 --> 00:38:55,100
I don't know this woman.

